

<header id="home-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row"
      <div class="col-lg-12"
      <div class="container">
      <%= link_to "The Firepit", '#', id: "logo" %>
       <p class="login pull-right">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <%= link_to "Logout", destroy_user_session_path,:method => :delete, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
          <% else %>
          <%= link_to "Login", user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
          <% end %>
       </p>
      </div>
      </div>
       
      </div>
    </div>
  <div class="container">
        <div class="row"
        <div class="col-lg-12"
        <div class="header-description">
            <h2>Welcome to the Firepit!</h2>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to "Start New Pit", new_pit_path, class: "btn-default-start" %>
            <br>
            <%= link_to "Join Existing Pit", pits_path, class: "btn-default-join" %>
            <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Join the Pit!", new_user_registration_path, class: "header-btn" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="header-features">
            <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 header-feature">
              <h3><i class="icon-random"></i> &nbsp;Specific topics with specific people</h3>
              <p>Start a topic with a book, video, or just and idea you have. Then invite and discuss</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 header-feature">
              <h3> <i class="icon-group"></i> &nbsp;Share and discuss around our digital fire</h3>
              <p>Since the dawn of time, great ideas have manifested themselves and been discussed around the fire. It's no wonder then that creating a digital version of such discussions is a must in our day and age</p>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</header>